{"tid":818223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗議無償加班　企業在英國發起「4點鐘收工日」","createTime":"2018-09-14T03:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T06:04:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":96,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d4e87eae41f21c129457aadfd9bf97cd70010c","tid":818223,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T03:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180914/s00005/5a99cae0b51983d49603e19b12d03e9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180914%2Fs00005%2F5a99cae0b51983d49603e19b12d03e9e.jpg&h=e7f5f853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港打工仔想下午4點鐘收工看似遙不可及，有能量飲品公司在英國發起「4點鐘收工日」，呼籲打工仔今日早一小時下班，抗議無償加班。<br />\n<br />\n今年初一項調查顯示，英國500萬名僱員每周無償超時工作約7小時，上班前後更要回覆電郵，每年超時工作價值相等於310億英鎊。有能量飲品公司發起將今日（14日）定為「全國4點鐘收工日」，呼籲僱員今日盡早完成工作後，向僱主提出早一小時下班，藉此增加生產力，「完成工作後去享受更重要的事情吧，例如好好享受周末。」公司稱不僅僱員會受惠，僱主亦會因僱員工作效率上升而得益。<br />\n<br />\n英國勞工政策訂立最高工時，又制定最低休息時間及假期，部分規定如下：<br />\n<br />\n每周最多工作48小時<br />\n每日至少要有連續11小時休息<br />\n每年有至少28日有薪年假<br />\n每工作6小時至少有20分鐘休息時間<br />\n晚間僱員每日最多工作8小時<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180914/s00005/1536891374087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180914%2Fs00005%2F1536891374087&d=rAai0gMwKAq3%2B1w65DxwjKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ee3d7de8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180914%2Fs00005%2F1536891374087&h=7f4ebfbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180914/s00005/1536891374087</a>"},{"pid":"2c0bd2ae8a2e280b93b7e70a8db4014bf79dfd89","tid":818223,"uid":55917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae2b33712c00f58ea16f47e5